ELVIS AND JUNE: A LOVE STORY
Monday, January 20, 8pm / 7CT

Biography: Elvis & June: A Love Story traces Elvis' rise to fame in 1956 from 
the perspective of 18-year-old June Juanico, Elvis' first fiancée--before 
Priscilla!

Elvis and June met in the Spring of '55, before Elvis was nationally famous. A 
chance meeting one year later would blossom into a romance that led to 
engagement. Now for the first time, here is June's intimate true story... Why 
was Elvis crazy for June? How did fame change Elvis? What ultimately ended 
their relationship? This is a very personal view of 21-year-old Elvis-at the time 
he was changing the world of entertainment...and the world was also changing 
him! 

